I've finished my work on this wonderful dress knit from silken-cotton cord by Divina from @luckylama_wools  in ecological greens-themed colours. A little word regarding the material. It's soft and cooling, perfectly suits our NYC-heat. It was easy to knit, of great quality without neps. I've used 950 gr for the full dress, the cord is quite thick, yet the feeling it gives is light and free. As we say in America, put and go for it. Here with a great broche from #dsquared2, wonderful bag by #balline, a gift from my close friend. Ready, set, go!
